Entries.default: "Quite a party. Can't wait to meet our host."
"Set me loose on those drums and you would hear true rhythm."
"I'm afraid I'm not dressed for the occasion."
"Fantastic. I've got five flakes on kith sacrifice. Any takers?"
"If my folks were still alive, they'd never believe the things I've seen."
"Hey, how high does this thing go, anyway? We're gonna run out of mountain soon."
